	<string>## Usage

Search your paired bluetooth devices via the `btd` keyword. Press &lt;kbd&gt;↩&lt;/kbd&gt; to reverse a device’s state (on becomes off, and vice-versa).

![Connect of disconnect devices](images/about/btd.png)

Toggle bluetooth as a whole via the `btt` keyword. Configure the [Hotkey](https://www.alfredapp.com/help/workflows/triggers/hotkey/) for faster toggling.

